
List packages by installation date

# tail -f /var/log/dpkg.log
$ sudo tail -f /var/log/dpkg.log

# less /var/log/dpkg.log
# more /var/log/dpkg.log



See package installation date and time

# grep installed /var/log/dpkg.log


